Introduction
============

This is a simple test to reproduce an issue that we have observed with
riak_search.  Please see the riak.png file in this directory to get
an idea of the observed issue.

Prerequisites
=============

1.  riaksearch (https://github.com/basho/riak_search/)
2.  the riak python client (https://github.com/basho/riak-python-client)
3.  matplotlib (which requires numpy)


Setup
=====

1.  check/edit the config.py file
2.  install search hook
    search-cmd install test
3.  clear the schema cache
    search-cmd clear-schema-cache

Testing
=======

python multi-mechanize.py riak_test
